  criteriaText={"Trip estimates are per person from Delhi via Indira Gandhi International (DEL). The origin follows the busiest-airport methodology for this region. The order is the ranking. Higher means rarer globally, more mind-expanding or harder to replace with a similar trip. Estimates assume economy flights where needed, midrange lodging, meals, local transfers, required fees and the shortest realistic visit."}
